{
  "stem": "14897.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And but I-- you know, I remember that I was always the initiator of all such things, so--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were well off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, I told you, was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, his patients came from all different levels of society.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mostly, they were Jews, but there were some non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, I remember that at one point during the war, we met a Polish man who turned out to have been my father's patient.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he worked-- there was no Medicaid in Poland, so most doctors had private patients, paying patients, and the rates would differ depending on the ability to pay.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they also did a lot of pro bono work, and almost pro bono work through clinics, et cetera, and so my father did the same kind of things, all kinds.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He specialized in bacteriology.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had the laboratory right in the apartment where we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he performed all the different analysis, different tests.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His avocation, though, was research.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was always trying to make something out of something else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if he didn't need to make a living, I think he would have been kind of a basic research person-- which by the way, interestingly enough, my oldest son is.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's a molecular biologist and likes to do basic research.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, more in my father's, really, than mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my life changed very abruptly at 4 o'clock in the morning on September 1, 1939 when the first bombs fell on Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- there were, of course, intimations of the coming troubles, naturally, in Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I knew, being 11 and a 1/2-- I didn't really understand it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a child, I really was in many ways, much more naive then an 11 and a 1/2 year old would be in United States.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
